snippet.textDisplay: Coming from the medical world, a lot of people have to drink this because they can't swallow properly with due to CVAs and strokes. Mixing thickener into coffee, juice, water, and so on helps them live semi normal lives without aspirating (choking) on fluids and dying. I'm hoping this video doesnt somehow promote the idea that people really SHOULDN'T be drinking this and end up telling their loved ones that are prescribed this diet that they shouldnt drink it. Please stay informed and be aware that these prescriptions are needed for those who cannot swallow thin liquids.
